            <h2>Embedded Google Map (iFrame)</h2>
            <div class="ratio ratio-16x9">
                <iframe title="ABC Retailers Location"
                        loading="lazy"
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=1%20Adderley%20St%2C%20Cape%20Town&output=embed"
